# Input

```scss
html[lang=/* biome-ignore format: keep raw */#{$locale}]{color:red;}
html[lang=#{$locale}/* biome-ignore format: keep raw */]{color:blue;}

```


# Formatted

```scss
html[lang=/* biome-ignore format: keep raw */ #{$locale}] {
	color: red;
}
html[lang=#{$locale} /* biome-ignore format: keep raw */] {
	color: blue;
}

```
